description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Registered Learning Disability Nurse (RNLD)&lt;/strong&gt; with a passion for delivering the best quality of care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be working 42 hours per week at Cygnet Acer Clinic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cygnet Acer Clinic&lt;/strong&gt; is our 28 bed rehabilitation service providing assessment, treatment and rehabilitation for women with personality disorder and complex needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Day-to-Day…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise an allocated team of Nurses and Support Workers and ensure care and associated duties are allocated effectively and within team members’ competence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be responsible for the co-ordination, assessment, planning, implementation and evaluation of individual Patient programmes of care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and monitor managerial and clinical supervision within the allocated team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor staff rotas to ensure effective staffing on shifts with due regard to skill and gender mix. Inform the Head of Care of any shortfalls or issues that may affect patient care and safety&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct Return to Work and Sickness interviews, at the request of the Head of Care. Ensure appropriate documentation is maintained&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report any ill health amongst Patients and make requests for RC / GP / Professional visits where necessary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in Staff and Patient meetings and attend training sessions as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Cygnet? We’ll offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS and employee discount scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;50% NMC registration renewal paid by Cygnet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free meals on duty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RCNi membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bespoke career pathways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company paid Life Assurance scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Smart Health Toolkit- Providing you with Fitness Programmes, Nutrition consultation and Health checks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will have…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced Registered Learning Disability Nurse (RNLD) with a current Pin Number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to maintain documentation, undertake audits and demonstrate integrity in your role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Well informed of the Mental Health Act 1983 &amp; have an understanding of latest nursing practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A commitment to patient recovery in order to effectively monitor, manage and reduce risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Compassion, resilience and a dedication to empower and support service user independence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desirable:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to deputise in a management role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An interest in leadership, research and assessment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cygnet Health Care&lt;/strong&gt; has been providing a national network of high quality specialist mental health services for 30 years.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cygnet Acer Clinic&lt;/strong&gt; islocated in &lt;strong&gt;Chesterfield&lt;/strong&gt;. It is a 28 bed rehabilitation service providing assessment, treatment and rehabilitation for women with personality disorder and complex needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rehabilitation is provided in a therapeutic environment, with a level of security matched to individual needs. The aim of the treatment, rehabilitation and re-socialisation programme is to prepare the people in our care either for transfer to conditions of lesser security, or for a life in the community&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here at&lt;strong&gt; Acer Clinic&lt;/strong&gt; we will support you in working towards your specific career goals, with new responsibilities and training opportunities that will ensure you develop professionally and personally every day. If you are ready for a step up in your career, choose an organisation with the vision to take you further.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What next?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you care about making a difference – we want to talk to you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Click the link to apply.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
